<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-1551] Add reopen(IndexCommit) methods to IndexReader</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-1551</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Add reopen(IndexCommit) methods to IndexReader to be able to reopen an index on any previously saved commit points with all advantages of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-1483&quot; title=&quot;Change IndexSearcher multisegment searches to search each individual segment using a single HitCollector&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LUCENE-1483&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Similar to open(IndexCommit) &amp;amp; company available in 2.4.0.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Any&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
            <key id="12415930">LUCENE-1551</key>
